{
  "texts": [
    "Speech-Text-SpeechWhen it handles speech, Generative AI is also only derivatively phonological.",
    "To be included in the LLM as a source text, or when a prompt is oral, speech must first be transliterated into text.",
    "Then if the Generative AI response is oral, transliteration needs to occur back from text to speech.",
    "In this process, the characteristic meaningful features of speech are mostly lost including prosody, dialect, gesticulation, embodied context, redundancy, hesitation, circumlocution, and more.",
    "In any event, LLMs are biased towards the grammar of written text if for no other reason than most of their sources are published and digitized writing."
  ]
}